{"tid":2033143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講到國安法咁自由，點解陳秋實尋求真相俾人拉？","createTime":"2020-05-24T12:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T14:03:55.000Z","uid":148551,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d3db173b1e5683eed33a5445062528895875393d","tid":2033143,"uid":148551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"先唔好講陳秋實係唔係鬼<br />\n佢做嘅嘢就係尋求真相 <br />\n佢冇反中國 冇犯法 又冇造謠言<br />\n講到明只會講佢親眼見到嘅新聞<br />\n但係最尾都被失蹤咗<br />\n<br />\n呢個可唔可以作為例子<br />\n講點解唔好相信國安法所謂嘅自由<br />\n因為即使你冇觸及任何法例<br />\n只要你靠近佢哋嘅真相<br />\n就會俾人告<br />\n<br />\n所以即使佢係唔係鬼都好 <br />\n對家點樣解釋到一個咁愛國嘅青年 咁樣都會俾人拉？"},{"pid":"3e7336481a676ffdb073712c86f8f679b5401992","tid":2033143,"uid":148551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea0e3ea225cebe512972cb3745ccaa40c2eb433","tid":2033143,"uid":262480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"常理冇得同佢地拗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一句話搞事已經拉得"},{"pid":"63f5dbb1898f562d28c218f1080787241241817e","tid":2033143,"uid":148551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ea0e3ea225cebe512972cb3745ccaa40c2eb433","tid":2033143,"uid":262480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"常理冇得同佢地拗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一句話搞事已經拉得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"我啲屋企人仲話緊你唔犯法人哋唔搞你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1550c8943d1c2d4b100d84fa13570492ac94ae59","tid":2033143,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:26:30.000Z","msg":"因為太多人知真相會顛覆國家"},{"pid":"02042aba42197e66a15629927d123e550c0f442c","tid":2033143,"uid":236878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AygYiNt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAygYiNt.jpg&h=f8e8da50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓主00後？"},{"pid":"9ebe2bd70ea481610de15f4acfb0f8b95f864389","tid":2033143,"uid":161781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63f5dbb1898f562d28c218f1080787241241817e","tid":2033143,"uid":148551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ea0e3ea225cebe512972cb3745ccaa40c2eb433","tid":2033143,"uid":262480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"常理冇得同佢地拗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一句話搞事已經拉得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"我啲屋企人仲話緊你唔犯法人哋唔搞你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:34:05.000Z","msg":"無logic既人好難同佢地解釋<br />\n不過如果你想同你屋企人講，可以試下同你屋企人解釋：<br />\n咁犯法既「法」係邊個定？中共定既，咁咪姐係中共唔鍾意你，佢就可以定條法例出黎搞死你 / 用現行法例顛覆國家政權 / 尋釁滋事呢種模稜兩可既罪名黎入你罪囉<br />\n你仲可以同佢解釋中共既政治理論。中共講既人民民主專政，將呢個國家既人分成2種：人民同反動派。所謂人民民主專政，就係佔多數（中共認為）既人民內部有民主，而對少數既反動派專政。人民有人權，反動派無。咁點樣分人民同反動派？從來都無明確既定義，黨話你係就係。所以個道理係一樣既，總之如果黨掌握左最後既話語權，條法例就一定信唔過"},{"pid":"a3b021c87ca7498f10ba5426e25e7f2d8f33fa2c","tid":2033143,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9a9609f4a9ead982dee0f720f361a590a8eabe69","tid":2033143,"uid":148551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ebe2bd70ea481610de15f4acfb0f8b95f864389","tid":2033143,"uid":161781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63f5dbb1898f562d28c218f1080787241241817e","tid":2033143,"uid":148551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ea0e3ea225cebe512972cb3745ccaa40c2eb433","tid":2033143,"uid":262480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"常理冇得同佢地拗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/